<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background:rgb(230, 218, 218);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .otp-box {
            background: #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">OTP Verification</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{ name }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to verify your email. Use the OTP below to proceed:</p>
            <div class="otp-box">{{ otp }}</div>
            <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Do not share it with anyone for security reasons.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Your Company. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
